      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MINTER SCORCH (7) has been out of the placings the last couple but was a Special conditions H winner (24.60) three back at this track. Can make amends this time. ROYAL PRIDE (2) was never in contention last time at this track, but prior to that won comfortably by 4 lengths at this track (24.58) beating Newbrock Tilly in a Grade 5 on February 18. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Should be thereabouts. ROMP TIN (6) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (24.72) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record here including four wins. Should be in this for a long way. LUCA SKYWALKER (4) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
